n-of-state parameter w to vary, we find $\gamma$ = 0.73 ± 0.28 and w = -1.007 ± 0.065, demonstrating that the expansion and the growth histories are consistent with a $\Lambda$CDM universe ($\gamma$ = 0.55; w = -1).},
