at these data indirectly support, {\{}OMEGA{\}}{\_}0{\_} = 0.24 +/- 0.05 +/- 0.09, where the errors are, respectively, the 1 $\sigma$ random error and an estimate of the possible systematic error resulting from the normalization to galaxy content.},
